bination with other agents that are potentially hepatotoxic (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/96156/', '', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Amprenavir, Simeprevir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Cabotegravir, Lenacapavir, More', 'Pemetrexed, Cladribine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Nelarabine, Fludarabine, Decitabine, Azacitidine, Capecitabine', 1767369485);
